STATE
v.
Willie M. JACKSON. No. 486P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 11, 2004. Steven F. Bryant, Assistant Attorney General, Valerie M. Pittman, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 22nd day of September 2004 by Kimberly A. Swank to Withdraw as Counsel:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 11th day of October 2004."
